From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: tim2tox-bootstrap <bootstrap@local>
Date: Wed, 20 May 2026 07:28:00 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 9/9] V2TimGroupInfo.fromJson: tolerate missing
 add-option, approve-option, and self-info fields

Three null-cast crashes in `V2TimGroupInfo.fromJson` were aborting the
callback dispatch (via the outer try/catch in
`NativeLibraryManager._handleNativeMessage`) every time a getGroupsInfo
result was deserialized on the binary-replacement path.

Symptom observed in tim2tox auto_tests Phase 4:
`scenario_group_topic_revert_virtual_test (setUpAll) [E]`
  type 'Null' is not a subtype of type 'int'
  v2_tim_group_info.dart 69:57   new V2TimGroupInfo.fromJson
or
  type 'Null' is not a subtype of type 'Map<String, dynamic>'
  v2_tim_group_info.dart 88:26   new V2TimGroupInfo.fromJson

The C++ side (`ffi/dart_compat_group.cpp`) emits a minimal group-info
JSON that does not always include `group_detail_info_approve_option`,
`group_detail_info_add_option`, or `group_base_info_self_info`. These
fields are also absent on the Tencent native SDK in some legitimate
cases (e.g., groups the local user is not a member of, public groups
queried by ID), so a defensive default is the correct shape rather
than the C++ side fabricating the keys.

Fix (mirrors the pattern of 0007 v2-tim-message-risk-type-null-safety):

  - `approveOpt` / `groupAddOpt`: cast to nullable int with a `?? 0`
    fallback before passing into `cGroupAddOption2DartEnum`, which
    expects a non-nullable int.
  - `jsonGroupSelfInfo`: when `group_base_info_self_info` is absent or
    not a Map, treat as an empty map so the subsequent
    `jsonGroupSelfInfo['group_self_info_*']` reads return null (which
    each `?` / nullable field already accepts) instead of crashing.

After this fix, all Phase 4 group virtual tests except
`scenario_group_message_virtual_test` (which has an unrelated Tox
group-message delivery issue) pass.
---
 lib/models/v2_tim_group_info.dart | 9 ++++++---
 1 file changed, 6 insertions(+), 3 deletions(-)

diff --git a/lib/models/v2_tim_group_info.dart b/lib/models/v2_tim_group_info.dart
--- a/lib/models/v2_tim_group_info.dart
+++ b/lib/models/v2_tim_group_info.dart
@@ -66,7 +66,7 @@

   V2TimGroupInfo.fromJson(Map json) {
     json = Utils.formatJson(json);
-    approveOpt = EnumUtils.cGroupAddOption2DartEnum(json["group_detail_info_approve_option"]).index;
+    approveOpt = EnumUtils.cGroupAddOption2DartEnum((json["group_detail_info_approve_option"] as int?) ?? 0).index;
     groupID = json['group_detail_info_group_id'] ?? '';
     groupType = GroupType.convertGroupTypeEnum(json['group_detail_info_group_type'] ?? 0);
     groupName = json['group_detail_info_group_name'];
@@ -77,7 +77,7 @@
     owner = json['group_detail_info_owner_identifier'];

     createTime = json['group_detail_info_create_time'];
-    groupAddOpt = EnumUtils.cGroupAddOption2DartEnum(json['group_detail_info_add_option']).index;
+    groupAddOpt = EnumUtils.cGroupAddOption2DartEnum((json['group_detail_info_add_option'] as int?) ?? 0).index;
     lastInfoTime = json['group_detail_info_last_info_time'];
     lastMessageTime = json['group_detail_info_last_msg_time'];
     memberCount = json['group_detail_info_member_num'];
@@ -85,7 +85,10 @@
     isSupportTopic = json["group_detail_info_is_support_topic"];
     isEnablePermissionGroup = json["group_detail_info_enable_permission_group"] ?? false;

-    Map<String, dynamic> jsonGroupSelfInfo = json["group_base_info_self_info"];
+    final dynamic rawSelfInfo = json["group_base_info_self_info"];
+    final Map<String, dynamic> jsonGroupSelfInfo = rawSelfInfo is Map
+        ? Map<String, dynamic>.from(rawSelfInfo)
+        : <String, dynamic>{};
     role = jsonGroupSelfInfo['group_self_info_role'];
     joinTime = jsonGroupSelfInfo['group_self_info_join_time'];
     unreadMsgCount = jsonGroupSelfInfo['group_self_info_unread_num'];
